{"title":"娄山关","authors":["高深"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":8,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"娄山关"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（回族）高深"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“娄山关”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻在一块很坚硬的石头上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深刻在一个民族的心坎上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一段染血的历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一册沉默的教科书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为昨天和明天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立一座碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默立碑前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涛声炮声号声马蹄声……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国命运的合声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注满耳鼓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最最悲壮的是劲烈的西风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和长空的雁鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里有太多脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分不清哪些是今人的造访"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪些是当年的征程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些矮脚马踏出的蹄迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在共和国的法典上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下不灭的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不讲述那些战斗细节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故事在阳光里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故事在雨丝里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故事在血管里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个很平凡的情节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都让人心热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个大字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给后人留下万千追念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦难在这里走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死亡在这里走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望在这里走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利在这里走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一出动人的大戏从这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进入高潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个恒久的主题从这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"获得认同"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅仅标明一段地界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还永永远远地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一段辉煌的历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉说……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}